@startuml
title deleteBoard

actor User
participant BoardController
participant BoardCommandService
participant BoardCommandRepository
participant DomainEventPublisher

participant PermissionContextAPI as "권한검사 API \n(외부 Bounded Context)"

User -> BoardController : DELETE /board/{boardId}
BoardController -> BoardCommandService : deleteBoard(boardId, userId)

BoardCommandService -> PermissionAPI : GET /internal/permissions?userId={userId}&boardId={boardId}&action=DELETE_BOARD
PermissionContextAPI --> BoardCommandService : HTTP 200 OK / 401 Unauthorized / 403 Forbidden / 404 NotFound

alt HTTP 200 OK
    BoardCommandService -> BoardCommandRepository : findById(boardId)
    BoardCommandRepository --> BoardCommandService : Board

    BoardCommandService -> BoardCommandRepository : delete(Board)
    BoardCommandService -> DomainEventPublisher : publish(BoardDeletedEvent)

    BoardCommandService --> BoardController : HTTP 200 OK
else HTTP 401 / 403 / 404
    BoardCommandService --> BoardController : 상태 코드 전달
end

BoardController --> User : HTTP 응답 반환
@enduml